responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "EBAC7DF14A194901103EA68209DEAECD", "There are answers to the mystery of Aeterna in the Sandsquall, and they may very well rest in this tomb at the foot of the figure\'s flowing gown. The crypt holds the whispers of a forgotten past, and we who seek it may find our way in. It\'s what I gather from the inscription on the door, \"May the Exalted Oracles rest in the favored shade of Aeterna\'s eternal grace.\"")
name: EVT_SAN_0008_AeternasClimb_Priest_Success_DLG_3_Response
